quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  76,1,"Nummah seehadaytut rooci haanak duma dabaanak xer (der) daban kaal tatre, usuk cusaanamay xagar kak xagaanah tuh suge kalah"
  76,2,"Diggah nanu seehadaytu lab num kee say numuk yengele daacoytih tiffak kaa ginne kaa naqayyaruh, (mokkorruh) tokkel yaabbeeh yable seehadaytu kaa abne"
  76,3,Diggah nanı tirtô gitaa kee makô gita kaah baxxaqisneh moomintuy faatita akkee kee korostay yangadde akke yakke immay
  76,4,"Diggah nanu korosuh, silsilootay ibitte keenik edde debraanaa kee, ogoogay fillittee kee gaboobi ittat keenik edde yaxeenii kee, saqiir deqsitta giráy ken carrisa keenih massosne"
  76,5,Diggah meqe mari galoosay gocoyuk (kamri) kibuk taniy agleh kaafuur lek yaaquben
  76,6,"Ama gocoyuy yaaqubeeniy kaafuur agleh edde yani, is daray Yallih naqoosa kak taaqube, usun ayfuxxukiyyah tet yayfuxxukeeniih, faxxa heen kabul tet beyan"
  76,7,"Ama mari axbuux (nadri) duudusaah, Qhiyaamah ayróy umaané kak fixiixih tani Yallih digaalák meesitan"
  76,8,Kaadu usun tumaliiy qayxixxuu kee seewaytu maaqó yaskamen tet kacanu luk
  76,9,"Cagalah nanu sin kah naskamem Yallih foocih taaga, galtoo kee faatit siinik elle mafanna iyyan"
  76,10,"Diggah nanu ninni Rabbik meesitna, gibdah fooci edde ribbiima (kamadima) ayrók (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk)"
  76,11,"Tokkel Yalli woo ayróh umaanék ken reebiseeh, fooci ifuu kee wallé (farcat) keenih yecee"
  76,12,Kaadu yisbireenimih sabbatah jannat kee cariiril ken galte
  76,13,"Kay addal qaraakiyil kelitak, ayró mayablaanaay, kaxxa xabca mayablan"
  76,14,"Kaadu Kay cooxih silaaló keenit xayyowtah ken silaalisak, kaadu ama cooxih mexexih mafaala xabbacoowiyyah keenih xabbacowta"
  76,15,"Kaadu jannatti urruy ken yakdume keenit meekisah, mingiilay lakqok tanii kee kobboyyaayiy bililleelak (karaarit kinnuk) tani"
  76,16,Bililleelay lakqok taniy usun elle faxaanah gidel kiyaasiyyah kiyaaseeni
  76,17,Kaadu kay addal galoosay gocoyuk kibuk taniy agleh zanjabiil lek ken yafqen
  76,18,"Kay addal tan daray, salsabiil deqsittak yaaquben"
  76,19,"Kaadu jannatti urruy elle yanin caalatal elle waara keenit meekita, ken table waqdi luuluy fixiixiseeni ken takka le"
  76,20,"Kaadu jannatak faxe ikkeey wagittay, tokkel niqmatay weeloysoonu duude waanaa kee kaxxa Reeda table"
  76,21,"Anxaxin saray xabcin cariirik yanii kee gibdi cariirik yan sari ken xagaral yaniih, qado lakqok tan gabâ biriitat (cagooluk) billiiman, kaadu ken Rabbi yaaqubeenimiy saytuniy taahirik tanik ken yafqe"
  76,22,"Diggah ta galtó sin meqe taamoomih galto kinniih, sin taamoomi addunyal yalli raabiteeh yikcineh yan taamak sugte keenik iyyan"